{"tid":2136583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"定單疫情成正比 車手無奈","createTime":"2020-08-02T09:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T10:47:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52f9ed0972c0b0a91c069956e967f543cbd8df20","tid":2136583,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/LT6OV3BCF6FHSYUMFRF6EUNTVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FLT6OV3BCF6FHSYUMFRF6EUNTVU%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAncbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=98283c76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FLT6OV3BCF6FHSYUMFRF6EUNTVU%2F&h=28a2cda1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/LT6OV3BCF6FHSYUMFRF6EUNTVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n定單疫情成正比 車手無奈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gQOFLef2MgmREQVfO-85s8Av4eM=/634x418/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ROC5SRXHTXUNDE25O3SXZ5Z7BI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgQOFLef2MgmREQVfO-85s8Av4eM%3D%2F634x418%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FROC5SRXHTXUNDE25O3SXZ5Z7BI.gif&h=7bb4f622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n糖水店少東高人傑每晚透過電話或短訊接定單。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】4月自組外賣團隊的糖水店少東阿傑自嘲計劃是「癡人說夢」，幸獲友人支持。車手之一的阿峰（22歲）日間於地盤駕駛七人車，從沒送外賣經驗，三個月前見到阿傑於fb招募外賣車手便毛遂自薦，家住天水圍的他坦言不熟港島路段經常迷路，「扣埋來回隧道費賺得2、30蚊」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：亞博啟用收30患者 走廊漏水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n街市小店斥政府「唔專業」<br />\n<br />\n阿峰指6月底疫情緩和，市民外出用膳增加，經常整晚沒定單，如今疫情來勢洶洶令定單增加不少，但他對於確診個案同步增加感到無奈，坦言若需送外賣到黄大仙、慈雲山等重災區，盡量不上樓且每次會以酒精消毒雙手。<br />\n<br />\n同樣靠外賣幫補生意的，還有翠林街市內的食店「S.T泰坊」。泰國。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「呢班後生仔真係好好，好感激佢哋！」對於防疫政策朝令夕改，小月難掩不滿：「好似咩都試吓咁，唔專業囉，攞我哋條命嚟博！」"},{"pid":"fe7c8c2409e8103929034244e98a3a993bd1f030","tid":2136583,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"蘋果啲人真係唔多識中文 訂單同定單都撈得"}]}